      "content": "but the zyrtec is right here and i kinda feel like it'll work since i always get itchy eyes with pollen. i'm just too tired to deal with a doctor right now. can i just take a double dose to make sure it kicks in fast? it's probably fine if i just stay inside for a bit.",
